            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段跟隨美股急彈 日指暫升逾1800點 韓股漲逾4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國道指昨晚急彈逾千點，帶動日韓等亞洲主要股市今早初段顯著回升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時12分，日經平均指數報52919點，升1856點或3.64%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫升239點或4.75%，報5292點；稍早前KOSPI 200期指已急漲5%而啟動熔斷機制，程序化交易暫停5分鐘。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15821609-%e6%97%a5%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%b7%9f%e9%9a%a8%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e6%80%a5%e5%bd%88-%e6%97%a5%e6%8c%87%e6%9a%ab%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1800%e9%bb%9e-%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e6%bc%b2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250804_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 08:15:03",
